  <summary date="2023-08-01T13:17:39Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Political Bias In Algorithm Sorting Emails Act of 2022 or the Political BIAS Emails Act of 2022

 This bill restricts email providers from applying filtering algorithms that label political campaign messages as spam and requires providers to publicly report on their email delivery practices.</summary>
